-- Green Dragon Gas Plans Share Sale for as Much as $450 Million, Times Says
-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 2010-11-08T02:53:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/green-dragon-gas-plans-share-sale-for-as-much-as-450-million-times-says.html
Green Dragon Gas Ltd. plans to list
its shares on the Hong Kong market by early next year, the
London-based Times reported, citing people close to the matter.  The company may seek to raise up to $450 million from the
Hong Kong listing, the newspaper said, citing the people. Green
Dragon specializes in Chinese coal-bed methane, the Times said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
